---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro"
import Button from "../components/Button.astro"
import Text from "../components/Text.astro"
import CTASection from "../components/CTASection.astro"

---

<MainLayout title="WebCharged Web Solutions" page="home">

  <section class="relative flex justify-center bg-blue-gradient px-32 md:px-53 lg:px-59 py-85 md:py-138 lg:py-249">
    <div class="grow-1 flex flex-col gap-53 lg:gap-36 max-w-1281">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-20 lg:gap-36">
        <h1 class="text-electric font-semibold text-28 md:text-33 lg:text-47 max-w-400 md:max-w-480 lg:max-w-672">Website design services built around your business</h1>
        <p class="text-parchment text-19 lg:text-21 max-w-496 lg:max-w-576">Custom websites designed for small businesses that need to stand out online and convert visitors into customers.</p>
      </div>
      <Button class="self-start" href="/project-planning-call">Start your project today</Button>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute -top-100 md:-top-147 lg:-top-181 right-0 pointer-events-none">
      <picture class="block lightning-graphic">
        <!-- Mobile: loads on screens 750px and under -->
        <source
          srcset="/images/yellow-lightning-bolt-360.webp"
          media="(max-width: 750px)"
          type="image/webp"
          width="360"
          height="676"
        >
        <!-- Desktop: default fallback -->
        <img
          src="/images/yellow-lightning-bolt.webp"
          title="Decorative yellow lightning bolt" 
          alt=""
          width="615"
          height="1152"
          fetchpriority="high"
          decoding="sync"
        >
      </picture>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center px-32 md:px-53 lg:px-95 py-53 md:py-95 gap-53 md:gap-59">
    <div class="grow-1 flex flex-col items-center max-w-480 md:max-w-1281 gap-32 md:gap-59">
      <h2 class="text-23 md:text-28 lg:text-36 text-blue text-center font-semibold">Why WebCharged?</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-32 md:gap-36">

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-9 md:gap-36">
          <div class="shrink-0 md:w-68">
            <span class="text-spark text-[5rem]/[120%] font-semibold">1.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-9">
            <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 text-blue font-semibold text-center md:text-start">You Are a Person, Not a Number</h3>
            <Text>
              We treat you like an individual person. 
              We are committed to understanding your unique thought process and how you define success. 
              This allows us to help you reach your goals.
            </Text>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-9 md:gap-36">
          <div class="shrink-0 md:w-68">
            <span class="text-spark text-[5rem]/[120%] font-semibold">2.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-9">
            <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 text-blue font-semibold text-center md:text-start">Honesty and Fairness</h3>
            <Text>
              If you don’t need the fanciest solution, we won’t make you think you need it. 
              We will offer you the best solution to help you thrive, 
              at prices that are reasonable for the value you receive.
            </Text>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-9 md:gap-36">
          <div class="shrink-0 md:w-68">
            <span class="text-spark text-[5rem]/[120%] font-semibold">3.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-9">
            <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 text-blue font-semibold text-center md:text-start">Reliability and Punctuality</h3>
            <Text>
              We’re punctual, and we meet deadlines. 
              We provide reliable solutions to your web-related needs. 
              For every web project, we first understand what you want. 
              Then we commit to complete that dream.
            </Text>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <Button href="/about-us">Learn more about us</Button>

  </section>
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center px-32 md:px-53 py-53 md:py-95 bg-charcoal">
    <div class="grow-1 flex flex-col max-w-480 md:max-w-840 gap-53">

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start gap-53 rounded-md md:border-[1.5px] border-electric md:p-59">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start gap-32">
          <h2 class="text-electric text-23 md:text-28 lg:text-36 font-semibold">Our web design service</h2>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-14">
            <Text class="text-parchment">We follow a predefined formula to create websites that actually convert visitors into customers.</Text>
            <Text class="text-parchment">When people visit your website, your website will do a great job of persuading them to become customers.</Text>
            <Text class="text-parchment">This means more customers and more sales. And <span class="text-electric font-semibold">this means increased revenue</span>.</Text>
          </div>
          <Text class="text-parchment">You'll get a website that you will be proud of. And this includes:</Text>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-22 md:mt-21">

            <div class="flex gap-9">
              <div class="shrink-0 flex px-4">
                <img class="h-24 md:h-32" src="/icons/brush-white.svg" alt="Brush icon">
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 md:py-2 lg:py-0">
                <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 text-parchment font-semibold">Custom design</h3>
                <Text class="text-parchment">Stand out from your competitors with a high-quality, beautiful design.</Text>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-9">
              <div class="shrink-0 flex px-4">
                <img class="h-24 md:h-32" src="/icons/speed-white.svg" alt="Website speed icon">
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 md:py-2 lg:py-0">
                <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 text-parchment font-semibold">Fast load speeds</h3>
                <Text class="text-parchment">Don’t scare visitors away with a slow-loading website. Instead, impress them.</Text>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-9">
              <div class="shrink-0 flex px-4">
                <img class="h-24 md:h-32" src="/icons/mobile-hand-white.svg" alt="Mobile phone icon">
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 md:py-2 lg:py-0">
                <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 text-parchment font-semibold">Mobile-friendliness</h3>
                <Text class="text-parchment">Give visitors an excellent impression of your business. (Most visitors will use a phone)</Text>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
        <Button mobileWidth={320} href="/custom-website-design">Learn more</Button>

      </div>
      <div class="w-full h-2 bg-parchment"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start gap-53 rounded-md md:border-[1.5px] border-electric md:p-59">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start gap-32">
          <h2 class="text-electric text-23 md:text-28 lg:text-36 font-semibold">Maintenance and support</h2>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-14">
            <Text class="text-parchment">
              We also provide website support for your website. 
              This way you can rest easy knowing that your website is in good hands. 
              We take care of any issues that arise with your website.
            </Text>
            <Text class="text-parchment">
              We will update it for you whenever you need to make a change. 
              Then you can be more efficient with your time, doing what you already do best. 
            </Text>
            <Text class="text-parchment">
              You'll be confident that your website is performing just as good as ever.  
            </Text>
          </div>
        </div>
        <Button mobileWidth={320} href="/website-support-plans">Get details</Button>

      </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center px-32 md:px-53 lg:px-95 py-53 md:py-95 gap-53 lg:gap-59">
    <div class="grow-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-32 md:gap-59 max-w-480 md:max-w-840 lg:max-w-1281">

      <h2 class="text-23 md:text-28 lg:text-36 font-semibold text-blue text-center">How we make a website</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-32 md:gap-53 lg:gap-36">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-14">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end gap-8 md:gap-21">
            <span class="text-40 md:text-47/[90%] lg:text-47/[95%] text-spark font-semibold">Phase 1<span class="hidden md:inline">:</span></span>
            <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 font-semibold text-blue">Gathering Information</h3>
          </div>
          <Text>
            We begin by understanding your business better. What do you do? 
            What makes you different? What are your goals? 
            Answering these questions and gathering other important details 
            is the foundation for a successful website project.
          </Text>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-14">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end gap-8 md:gap-21">
            <span class="text-40 md:text-47/[90%] lg:text-47/[95%] text-spark font-semibold">Phase 2<span class="hidden md:inline">:</span></span>
            <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 font-semibold text-blue">Ideation and Creation</h3>
          </div>
          <Text>
            We use the information we gathered from you to create designs that reflect your brand. 
            We develop these designs into a user-friendly, 
            working website that builds your customers’ confidence in your business.
          </Text>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-14">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end gap-8 md:gap-21">
            <span class="text-40 md:text-47/[90%] lg:text-47/[95%] text-spark font-semibold">Phase 3<span class="hidden md:inline">:</span></span>
            <h3 class="text-19/[120%] md:text-23 lg:text-27 font-semibold text-blue">Launch and Beyond</h3>
          </div>
          <Text>
            Your website is now complete! 
            We hand over all designs and materials we created for your website. 
            This phase marks the beginning of your business growth! 
            We also provide 12 months of free support so your website stays perfect.
          </Text>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>

    <Button href="/custom-website-design">View details and pricing</Button>

  </section>
  <CTASection>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-20 lg:gap-22">
      <h2 class="text-23 md:text-28 lg:text-36 font-semibold text-blue">Let's connect!</h2>
      <Text>Got an idea or question? Feel free to reach out and we’ll get back to you!</Text>
    </div>
    <Button class="self-start" href="/contact-us">Reach out to us</Button>
  </CTASection>

</MainLayout>


<style>

  @media screen and (max-width: 750px) {
    .special-button {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    .special-button a {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: fit-content;
      padding-inline: 44px;
      white-space: nowrap;

      &:hover, &:focus-visible, &:active {
        background: var(--color-spark-400);
      }
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 750px) {
    .lightning-graphic {
      position: relative;
      right: max(-222px, calc(-1 * (222px + (68.292px - 18.97vw))));
      width: 22.5rem;
    }
  }
  /* For Tablet Landscape */
  @media screen and (min-width: 751px) and (max-width: 1150px) {
    .lightning-graphic {
      position: relative;
      left: calc(160px + (150.2px - 20vw));
      width: 27.4375rem;
    }
  }
  /* For Laptop */
  @media screen and (min-width: 1151px) and (max-width: 1400px) {
    .lightning-graphic {
      position: relative;
      left: calc(306px + (763.6px - 66.4vw));
    }
  }
  /* For Desktop */
  @media screen and (min-width: 1401px) {
    .lightning-graphic {
      position: relative;
      left: max(27px, calc(140px + (518.7px - 37.05vw)));
    }
  }
</style>